fcitx: fcitx (input method for simplified Chinese)
fcitx:
fcitx: fcitx stands for Free Chinese Input Toy of X, an input method for
fcitx: Linux.  To be more precise, fctix is a collection of Simplified
fcitx: Chinese input methods based on XIM (X Input Method), including
fcitx: WuBi, PinYin, and QuWei, and it is distributed under GPL. It is
fcitx: the descendent of gWuBi.
